section(id="features", class="bg-primary bg-opacity-[3%] pt-[120px] pb-[50px]")
  div(class="container")

    div(class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-16px]")
      div(class="w-full px-4")
        div(class="mx-auto max-w-[570px] text-center mb-[100px] wow fadeInUp", data-wow-delay=".1s")
          h2(class="text-black dark:text-white font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-[45px] mb-4") Features at a Glance
          p(class="text-body-color text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed md:leading-relaxed")
            | Out of the box, Simplicity comes packed with a lot of features to ease development
            | and reduce development time.

    div(class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-16px]")

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".15s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/js
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") 100% JavaScript
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")= appName
            |  is built using JavaScript (Node.js).
            | That means your app can be built entirely with JavaScript
            | saving your team from switching between server and browser languages.

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/database
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") Supports multiple Datastores.
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")= appName
            |  supports a variety of datastores ranging from schemaful (explicit schema) to
            | schemaless (implicit schema) databases.
            | Supported databases include Maria DB, MySQL, Postgres, SQLite, and MongoDB.

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".25s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/rest-api
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") Auto-Generated REST APIs
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")
            | Jump start your backend code with sensible blueprints.
            | Thanks to Simplicity's automatic API generation,
            | You can build a full REST API backend while writing as minimal code as possible.

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".1s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/chrome-cast
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") Front-end agnostic
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")= appName
            | You can use Simplicity with any front-end framework such as Angular, React, Svelte, and Vue.
            | In addition, Simplicity supports back-end template engines like EJS, Mustache, Pug, etc.

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".1s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/layers
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") Versatile
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")= appName
            |  provides a robust and well-structured foundation for all your server-side application requirements.

      div(class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 px-4")
        div(class="mb-[70px] wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".1s")
          div(class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary bg-opacity-10 mb-10 text-primary")
            include /components/icons/di
          h3(class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-5") Dependency Injection
          p(class="text-body-color text-base leading-relaxed font-medium pr-[10px]")= appName
            |  comes with an easy to use but powerful dependency injection system
            | making application testing a breeze.
